    "name": "01 Data Services REST (Master Medical Data)",
    "description": "Provides product-related data and associated medical master data.\n\n##### **Available Endpoints**\n\n- Retrieve all records or only those modified since a given date _(delta management)_\n    \n- Retrieve a record by its identifier\n    \n- Retrieve records via simple search queries\n    \n\n##### **Available Entities**\n\n- Articles\n    \n- Companies\n    \n- Interactions\n    \n- Products\n    \n- Product Information\n    \n- Service Providers\n    \n- Value Sets\n    \n\n**Route to generate valid token : 01 Get and Save Token for Data Services REST (Master Medical Data)**",
